Are software engineers working for Google/Facebook incompetent?
text:
Read this before commenting Reference: https://wap.business-standard.com/article/international/too-many-employees-but-few-work-pichai-zuckerberg-sound-the-alarm-122080801425_1.html

This is not a troll question or a question asked to criticize Googlers/Meta employees.

Pichai and Zuckerberg are of the opinion that hardly few engineers at Google/Facebook are productive.

Their observation leads me to ask another question: Does this mean that engineers working for Google/Facebook are only good at memorizing Leetcode questions?

I expect an honest opinion from everyone.
